18#include <string>
19
20namespace ZXing {
21
22class BitArray;
23
24namespace Aztec {
25
26class Token
27{
28public:
29 void appendTo(BitArray& bitArray, const std::string& text) const;
30
31 static Token CreateSimple(int value, int bitCount) {
32 return {value, -bitCount};
33 }
34
35 static Token CreateBinaryShift(int start, int byteCount) {
36 return {start, byteCount};
37 }
38
39private:
40 short _value;
41 short _count; // is simple token if negative,
42
43public:
44 Token(int value, int count) : _value((short)value), _count((short)count) {}
45};
46
47} // Aztec
48} // ZXing
